 "xaTomu All~ayoli", "text_ar": "خَطْمُ اللَّيْلِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The first approach of night:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "like as one says"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^anofu All~ayoli", "text_ar": "اَنْفُ اللَّيْلِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) ―         -b3-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "xiTaAmN", "text_ar": "خِطَامٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".       -A2-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A thing, an affair,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a business, of magnitude."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(IAar, Th, K.) It is related in a trad. that Mohammad promised a certain man to go forth to him, and delayed to do so; and when he went forth, he"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 768}, {"kind": "text", "text": "said to him,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$agalaniY xaTomN", "text_ar": "شَغَلَنِى خَطْمٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A thing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of magnitude"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "occupied me so as to divert me"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; as though the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "m", "text_ar": "م"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "were a substitute for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "b", "text_ar": "ب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (IAar, Th, TA:) but IAth says that it may mean (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a thing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that withheld"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "me, or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "prevented"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "me, [see 1,] from going forth. (TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["JK", "S", "Msb", "K", "TA", "IAar", "Th"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}